HEADWORD: backpack
<hw>back"pack</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a bag carried on the back,
supported by straps looped over the shoulders.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> knapsack; rucksack; haversack.</syn>
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

